publishing:hasEndDecadePeriod
a
owl:ObjectProperty
rdfs:comment
Relating a publishing to the decade period the last volume is published in.
rdfs:domain
publishing:Publishing
rdfs:isDefinedBy
publishing:
rdfs:label
pubblicazione ha il periodo di decennio fino (it)
publication a la période de décennie de fin (fr)
publishing has end decade period (en)
Publizieren hat Endejahrzehntperiode (de)
skos:note
Through a series of N3-rules a year literal without the year digit is converted to its decade period with the respective calendar start and end date typed literal, and with the start and end Julian Day Number, to enable interval calculus for temporal reasoning.
